HEADWORD: Stepbrother
<hw>Step"broth`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A brother by the
marriage of one's father with the mother of another, or of one's mother
with the father of another.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

